Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:58.95,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,Gently devours you, body and soul
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:58.95,Song-JAP [720p],,0,0,0,,Yasashiku hamu wa anata no subete o
