Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:04.12,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,It's my guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:04.30,ED JP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur3\fad(150,150)}It's my guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:14.84,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,You notice me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:14.84,Song-JAP [720p],,0,0,0,,Kidzuku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:17.65,ED JP-ja,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}気づく　目を見開いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:17.26,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,With your eyes wide open,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:17.26,Song-JAP [720p],,0,0,0,,Me o mihiraiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.64,Song-ENG [720p],,0,0,0,,A faint blue as lifeless as concrete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:19.64,Song-JAP [720p],,0,0,0,,Honoaoi konkuriito
